Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Interfaces
  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Interfaces 
    Interface and Description
    me.unei.configuration.api.format.INBTString
    This interface does not serve any purpose and is now subject to removal.
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    me.unei.configuration.StaticInstance.StaticInstanceExposer.backup()
    You should never call this function unless you known exactly what you are doing.
    me.unei.configuration.api.fs.IPathComponent.IPathComponentsList.cleanPath()
    use FSUtils.cleanPath(IPathComponent.IPathComponentsList) instead
    me.unei.configuration.StaticInstance.StaticInstanceExposer.clear()
    You should never call this function unless you known exactly what you are doing.
    me.unei.configuration.api.format.INBTList.getList(int, byte)
    Magic value of type. Prefer using INBTList.getList(int, TagType).
    me.unei.configuration.api.format.INBTCompound.getList(String, byte)
    Magic value of type. Prefer using INBTCompound.getList(String, TagType).
    me.unei.configuration.api.format.INBTList.getTagTypeId()
    Magic value. prefer using INBTList.getTagType().
    me.unei.configuration.api.format.INBTTag.getTypeId()
    Magic value. prefer using INBTTag.getType().
    me.unei.configuration.api.format.INBTCompound.getTypeOf(String)
    Magic value. prefer using INBTCompound.getTypeOfTag(String).
    me.unei.configuration.api.fs.IPathNavigator.PathSymbolsType.tryDetectType(String)
    This won't detect the type for sure and can lead to data-reading errors.
